Class Doctor

java.lang.Object
model.HMSPersonnel
model.Doctor
public class Doctor extends HMSPersonnel
Represents a Doctor in the system. Inherits from the HMSPersonnel class to include basic personnel details such as name, contact information, etc., and adds specific information related to the doctor's specialty, medical license, date of joining, and years of experience.
